AccessModifier : 
*****************************
public 
private
protected
default


Encaptulation : 
******************
wrapping datamemeber and function member in single unit and secure data member
by private access modifier.
-data hiding
-security

Inheritance : 
******************
use one class proprty into another class

base ---> derived
parent--->child
super--->sub

Polymorphism
*******************
same name , many form
compiletime : methodoverloading 
runtime : methodoverriding

Abstraction : 
*******************
hiding implimantation and showing functionality

we can achieve abstraction using 2 diffrent ways
1 : abstract class : partial abstraction
contains both abstract and instance method

2 : Interface : 100% abstraction
constains only abstract method

abstract method : method without body
public void display();


Instance method : method with body
public void display()
{
	method body
}

